    h2 Notifyers
    p There are 2 variations of the notify elements. A default set and a light set.  Simply append <code>-light</code> to the end of any notify elements.

.row
  .col
    blockquote.blockquote.blockquote--warning
      .blockquote__header Make element dismissable.
      .blockquote__body
        | Add the class <code>.notify__dismissable</code> to the main element.
        | Also make sure to initialize the javasript function.

